# STACKS

FILO = first in last out


### PARTS/COMPONENTS OF A STACK
- Size
- Top/Last (last to enter stack)

### FUNCTIONS
- Push()
- Pop()
- Peek() -- returns the top element (the last added item) without removing it or modifying the stack's structure


